== Overview ==
This weapon fires a concentrated Pulse Beam capable of causing significant disruption to energy and shield systems within a small area.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Pulse Beam can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
